11.content:
Our story begins in bikini bottom, the water was cool as ever, the scallops were chirping, it was just a normal day like any other or so the residents thought...

Little did they know that overhead was a fishing boat, a small vessel with a crew of one, this is where you come in. You are a marine biologist, with a passion for aquatic wildlife, however since you were severely underfunded, you couldn't afford the propped tools that a biologist in your possession had, so you improvised, bringing a fishing rod with you, you would catch, study and released what you could. What you didn't realize was that a gigantic wave have formed behind you and knocked you into the sea.

Falling deeper into the water, you tried to claw your way to the surface, but found that despite your best efforts, the current was too strong and the waters swallowed you and everything went dark. Hours later you awoke on what looked like...

You decide to get the anthro squirrels help. Hopefully she won't think that your trespassing in her home or anything like that.

You stopped screaming and looked up to see the squirrel looking straight at you with a very annoyed look "Y'all Don't have to scream so loudly, Ah Could see ya!" the squirrel said annoyed. "Oh Sorry" you meekly apologize to the squirrel

The next thing you knew the squirrel reached down and grabbed you with her two digits. She brought you up all the way right in front of her buck teeth, you look down and see the fur covered breasts that the squirrel had. They were decently sized. "Ay Eyes Up Here" the squirrel yelled in a texen accent. "Sorry!" you apologized again as you look her in her face

"hmmmmmm, you look like a human, but your way to small! You might even be smaller than Plankton" the squirrel says as she inspects your body "Anyway what are you doin in my tree dome?" "I don't know, I just kinda woke up here" you say telling the truth, still a tad afraid.

The squirrel brought you closer to her eye and you became scared, the squirrel then smiled at you as she dropped you into her palm "Well why Didn't you say so, the name is Sandy Cheeks, and this is where i live"

What a 180 turn, she was angry before but now she seems kind. "Uh my name is (Insert Name), good to uh........meet you"

"Nice to meet you too, look I know your scared and you don't know what's happening, but don't worry we will figure this out, I promise" Sandy Reassured you, "but until then you will be ___________. Okay!"

114.content:
Waking up, you looked around. Were you on... wood? It was all curved, suddenly you realized you were on a massive... lobster cage?! Suddenly you heard some noise and ran as far as you could to one side and saw some fish walking in. Wait, walking?! Where were you? You looked up at a giant sign that read... "The krusty krab?!" You shouted in shock. This could only mean one thing.

Glancing at the footpath below you notice a pink starfish walking towards the restaurant. You considered jumping on him, or even calling for him, but quickly shot down these ideas. He could miss landing on the starfish, and who knew if the dimwitted starfish would hear him. Looking around, you noticed a smell and turned to face a chimney.

You climb the metal thing and look down, you see a grill with Burgers on it. Now there's something... It was risky, but if you were lucky you could get a burger cushion. It was perhaps riskier than jumping on someone, but it was easier. Which method do you choose to get down?

Sandy orders her food to go so she can take her Krabby Patties home to eat them. This could be your chance! But do you catch a ride on her food or somewhere on her body? her tail seems exposed enough. Sandy sets her food down on a table for a moment to check something on her suit. You have to make the choice now.

You jump into the box of Krabby Patties just as Sandy closes it up. It is dark, but you enjoy the warm smell of delicious Krabby Patties around you.
Back at the Treedome, Sandy sets the box down on her table. Then she opens up the box and the light blinds you for a moment. Sandy sure looks hungry. Without noticing you, Sandy picks up the Krabby Patty that you are on. What do you do?
